# Gemini streaming

## File

`services/geminiService.ts` — `generateNextSpinner(previousCode, previousId, onStreamUpdate)`.

## Contract

- Model: `gemini-3-flash-preview`
- `responseMimeType: application/json` with `responseSchema` (`mutationName`, `reasoning`, `p5Code`)
- Stream chunks → `onStreamUpdate(fullText)` for partial JSON UI
- Return `SpinnerData` with timing/token estimates

## Prompt constraints (do not remove without product sign-off)

- p5 instance `p`, 400×400 canvas, `p.clear()` (transparent, no `p.background()`)
- Seamless infinite motion (`p.millis()` / sine; avoid hard loop resets)
- Thick strokes for 32×32 cursor legibility
- Evolution: ~80% lineage / ~20% mutation when `previousCode` is set

## Changes

- Consult **gemini-js-genai** skill before API shape changes
- Keep `App.tsx` dual `Promise.all` streams working
- Typed errors: `catch (error: unknown)`, narrow with `instanceof Error`
